*Ostani* tu (Stay here).
On je *ostao* duže nego što je planirao (He stayed longer than he had planned).
Morate se *ostati* koncentrisani (You must stay focused).
On je *ostao* sa mnom (He stayed with me).
Ona se *ostala* u krevetu (She stayed in bed).
*Ostanite* tu dok ne dođem (Stay here until I come).